{"tid":1701524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（被罷工事前工作）凌晨好去塞狗鐵啦","createTime":"2019-11-09T06:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:54:19.000Z","uid":67505,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0721a6ea7827ab0a8a6eed9eddddca273e2f6bce","tid":1701524,"uid":67505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"冇錯11.11早上搞馬路係好緊要<br />\n但你知好多港豬依然搭港鐵返工放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等到早上頭班車開先做嘢好容易發生衝突，唔夠快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果大家有做過結界師，就知狗鐵拉左閘再鎖閘，容易過冇閂閘自己起路障<br />\n善用單車鎖、鋼膠甚至拉爆，佢可以搵人拆但都要時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁第一波攻勢就成功左<br />\n一群人逼住搭巴士<br />\n手足再搞路面交通<br />\n成功大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要搞狗鐵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要狗鐵拉閘未開頭班車嗰陣搞</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一憂慮係凌晨人少，行蹤好容易暴露，大家搵定位變身同反跟蹤"},{"pid":"d110c5e5df5b3d2997dfa877804343da2aa68aca","tid":1701524,"uid":67505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394da084edcbe50f284665e054882f0d1dcc5704","tid":1701524,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"94b2bc8ac49bcbad9c03b4e16894d2077e390345","tid":1701524,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-0